## 4. Architectural & Database Improvements
```mermaid
graph TD
    UI[React Components] --> Hooks[Custom Hooks: useOrders, useFinance, etc.]
    Hooks --> Service[Service layer e.g., orderService.js]
    Service --> Firestore[(Firestore Database)]
```
1.  **Introduce a Service Layer:** Isolate Firestore queries into distinct service classes (e.g. `src/services/orderService.js`) to decouple components and hooks from data fetching logic.
2.  **Field Inconsistencies:** Standardize audit attributes across collections (using `createdAt` and `updatedAt` instead of mixed labels like `date` and `timestamp`).

